ROI Land Investments Ltd: Company Profile - Bloomberg



































































  









Feedback















roi land investments ltd
Public Company









Company Profile
Sector: Financials
Industry: Real Estate
Sub-Industry: Real Estate Owners & Developers
ROI Land Investments, Ltd. operates a real estate investment company. The Company invests in residential properties and provides land development, permit application, and infrastructure development services. ROI Land Investments focuses on properties located in the province of Quebec.




Corporate Information
Address:

825 Blvd Lebourgneuf
Bureau 315
Quebec, QC G2J 0B9
Canada


