U.S. Securities and Exchange Commission (SEC) Filings








Home






ROI Land Investments, Ltd. is a OTCQB Public Traded company listed under the trading symbol of “ROII”
ROI Land Investments, Ltd. operates a real estate investment company. The Company invests in residential properties and provides land development, permit application, and infrastructure development services. Our mission is to become a successful land developer characterized by our specific, disciplined yet flexible revenue model consisting of acquiring, permitting, servicing and profit taking.
















 







