“We specialize in acquiring undeveloped land in areas that have a positive economic outlook and a housing shortage, a strategy that enables us to generate strong risk-adjusted returns. We appreciate your investment and continued support as we expand our portfolio and seek to maximize value for shareholders.”
















Stock Information








Home






ROI Land Investments Ltd. is listed on OTCQB: ROII
We are a U.S. public trading company on the OTCQB under the symbol of ROII. We remain on the outlook for new opportunities with special focus in North America but not limited to other markets subject to due diligence and/or suitability. We are a real estate land development company, characterized by our specific, disciplined yet flexible revenue model consisting of acquiring, permitting, servicing and profit taking. –





