ROI Land Investments








Home






ROI Land Investments Ltd. is a real estate company specialized in acquiring undeveloped land.
 We discover and uncover the opportunities of prime tracts with strong potential through our large network.
ROI acquires this precious land, obtains the necessary development permits,
outsources the development of the infrastructure and sells the subdivided land units to major, known regional developers.

ROI Business Model


1. Land Acquisition
Purchase land ready for development.


2. Entitlement
Work with municipalities to obtain the rights for infrastructures development.


3. Development
Outsourcing of the necessary technical and construction work.


4. Profit Taking
Exit through selling to large residential developers.






